# NETWORK::NETWORK_HAS_CONTROL_OF_NETWORK_ID

## Summary
Returns true if the local machine has ownership of the object with the specified network ID (included pending ownership change check)

## Parameters
* **NETWORK_INDEX** networkId

## Returns
* **BOOL**
